        "authorLine": "Sheng Chen, Xiao Huan, Chun-Zuan Xu, Su-Shan Luo, Chong-Bo Zhao, Hua-Hua Zhong, Xue-Ying Zheng, Kai Qiao, Yi Dong, Ying Wang, Chang-Yun Liu, Hua-Pin Huang et al.",
